Yo New Tab Dashboard is our answer to the fragmented and diverse needs of users who spend a lot of time browsing the Internet. From now on, the start page may be more than just a search bar with standard services, but more... or less! Everything is up to you.
Yo New Tab is a way to customize your new tab with unlimited options. Among the most interesting features, you can find the following:
Create folders with different bookmarks on the new tab as needed;
Search service added to the middle search box by https://www.hlhjapp.com/search;
Possibility to change the background of the start page / upload your own photos;
A large number of useful tools;
Yo New Tab is a unique start page where you can add an unlimited number of folders with bookmarks. Any bookmark or a group of them can be organized in a separate folder, create different folders with a large number of bookmarks by subject, task, user, etc. Rename them, copy, choose a background and organize bookmarks inside each folder. Upload a preview to easily browse through numerous bookmark folders.
Using the start page has never been easier. Yo New Tab is designed so that you can manipulate applications as needed and set their layout for more convenience. Place the most used applications in the middle of the page and the others at the bottom. With Yo New Tab, you can also place apps according to their functions.
We will continue to work hard to provide more rich services!
